import React from 'react'
import Navbar from '../components/Navbar/Navbar'
import { Outlet } from 'react-router-dom'

export default function MainLayout() {
  return (
    <>
     <CartContextProvider>
          <CategoriesContextProvider>
            <WishContextProvider>
            <RouterProvider router={router}/>
    
            </WishContextProvider>
    
    
           
    
          </CategoriesContextProvider>
    
        </CartContextProvider>
        <Navbar/>
   <Outlet/>
    </>
  )
}
